Prepare dressing. Whisk together orange juice, oil, vinegar, tarragon, orange zest, salt, mustard, and pepper in medium bowl. Set aside. Assemble salad. Combine lettuce, onions, and pomelos in large bowl. Toss with dressing and mound onto 4 plates. Fan out a quarter of the avocado on top of each and top with crabmeat and hazelnuts.